Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.78,0:00:15.34,Opening,,0,0,0,,My right hand holds a bowl of gold,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.34,0:00:19.79,Opening,,0,0,0,,And my left holds one of silver.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.79,0:00:24.46,Opening,,0,0,0,,Never one without the other,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.46,0:00:37.50,Opening,,0,0,0,,Two unseen bowls for each of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.50,0:00:45.98,Opening,,0,0,0,,The golden one is filled with joy,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.98,0:00:52.99,Opening,,0,0,0,,shining warmly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.99,0:00:57.99,Opening,,0,0,0,,Since we met, my golden bowl
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.99,0:01:05.06,Opening,,0,0,0,,cannot hold all my happiness and love.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.83,0:01:15.20,Opening,,0,0,0,,Golden joy, silver sadness,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.20,0:01:22.55,Opening,,0,0,0,,I would leave my past behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.55,0:01:27.28,Opening,,0,0,0,,For you, for the sake of love,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.28,0:01:34.22,Opening,,0,0,0,,I would empty the bowls of my past.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.75,0:02:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you heard? The campaign has become a landslide!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.35,0:02:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd never have believed this could happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.73,0:02:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,They say even some seniors have signed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.80,0:02:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What'll happen to members, like us?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.87,0:02:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What could she be thinking... Miya-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.30,0:02:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hush. Miya-sama is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.83,0:02:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.17,0:02:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The Sorority has the full support of the School Board.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.40,0:02:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Please keep quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.18,0:02:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it that worries you so?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.64,0:02:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You surprise me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.48,0:02:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Properly chosen members have nothing to worry about. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.52,0:02:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But... Miya-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.10,0:02:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This movement is spreading completely out of control!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.58,0:02:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Please try to relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.52,0:03:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Our Sorority is a long-held tradition.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.98,0:03:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing will become of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.16,0:03:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So, listen, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.50,0:03:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's discuss the opera we're presenting next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.88,0:03:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,31. The Bad Apple
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.47,0:03:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon! Class is starting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.76,0:03:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayashida-san, Kiryu-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.88,0:03:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Say... Nakaya-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.30,0:03:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you let us sign your sheet?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.50,0:03:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What! How can you say that, Hayashida-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.59,0:03:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You are all Sorority members, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.54,0:03:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If you sign, you'll be kicked out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.44,0:04:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't care about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.80,0:04:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,When you needed us... we weren't any help to you, Junko...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.11,0:04:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let me have your resignation before the week is out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.07,0:04:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Kiryu-san, Hayashida-san, help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.70,0:04:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You all can testify that I really did have a fever during exams. Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.67,0:04:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Since then, we've had our doubts about the Sorority...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.33,0:04:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We're sorry, Junko!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.45,0:04:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive us, Junko!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.44,0:04:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I never blamed you! Never!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.65,0:04:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Junko!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.88,0:04:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Junko!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.61,0:04:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,My Dear Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.87,0:05:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,"Substantial"... that's the word I'd choose, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.34,0:05:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Our school's complexion has undergone a substantial change.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.21,0:05:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm off to do petition work... so see you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.21,0:05:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye! See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.85,0:05:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiryu-san, Hayashida-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.10,0:05:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd like to have a word with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.06,0:05:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Come along with us, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.12,0:05:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.10,0:05:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What on earth do you mean by this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.65,0:05:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You signed! And you are members!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.33,0:05:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.57,0:05:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We... we will resign.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.29,0:05:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, we'll resign.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.53,0:06:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It would appear you underestimate us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.88,0:06:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If we allow such things to happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.63,0:06:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,...how can we maintain any order in the Sorority?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.30,0:06:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Not another word!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.47,0:06:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,This kind of behavior... is unbecoming.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.48,0:06:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Miya-sama! But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.35,0:06:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoever wants to sign, can sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.37,0:06:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave them alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.19,0:06:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You two, on the other hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.28,0:06:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,...shall, of course, be expelled from the Sorority.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.15,0:06:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And, we will take all records of your membership,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.96,0:06:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,...and erase them forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.11,0:06:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.26,0:07:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The way things are going, the Sorority is in great danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.48,0:07:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If... if the Sorority is abolished,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.76,0:07:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,...what will become of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.15,0:07:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll lose everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.59,0:07:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The lavish parties and tea ceremonies,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.00,0:07:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,...the opulent seasonal celebrations,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.48,0:07:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,...designated reserved seats at the cafeteria and library,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.23,0:07:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,...and the envious eyes of the lower classes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.98,0:07:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,All of this will be taken away from us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.61,0:07:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So... tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.55,0:07:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.63,0:07:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,How is Miya-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.81,0:07:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Miya-sama is as resolute as always,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.76,0:07:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,...and I have the utmost respect for her as head of the Sorority...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.97,0:07:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.48,0:07:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,"But"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.44,0:07:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,...there are times I just cannot figure her out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.37,0:07:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Just between you and me... I feel the same way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.55,0:07:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.62,0:07:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sometimes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.28,0:08:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Not taking action against those who abandon the Sorority is admirable,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.83,0:08:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,...but this movement is becoming so widespread!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.98,0:08:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Can she preserve the Sorority by maintaining such an attitude?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.55,0:08:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not going to be easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.39,0:08:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, look at how this all started.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.54,0:08:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It was because she had to have that girl, Misonoo Nanako, in the Sorority!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.68,0:08:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's the way she treats her, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.09,0:08:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something strange there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.03,0:08:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.11,0:08:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,...the thing between her and Misonoo Nanako.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.68,0:08:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Could we...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.90,0:08:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.94,0:08:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we sit together?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.70,0:08:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.01,0:08:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,11 people in one hour, this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.88,0:08:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Good progress! Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.37,0:08:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we take a break?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.86,0:08:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.76,0:08:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Look what time it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.37,0:09:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,My first class is PE. I have to run!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.52,0:09:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok, see you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.80,0:09:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Misonoo-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.16,0:09:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Mona Lisa-no-Kimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.37,0:09:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to look so frightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.21,0:09:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to ask you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.95,0:09:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it between you and Miya-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.38,0:09:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I said before, I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.60,0:09:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't make any sense of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.99,0:09:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Why was Miya-sama so insistent on having you as a member?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.97,0:09:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Surely you must know something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.28,0:09:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I really don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.90,0:09:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.81,0:09:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.26,0:09:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.27,0:09:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you're talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.81,0:09:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me. My class is starting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.37,0:10:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,My Dear Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.94,0:10:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,...when she asked me that time,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.15,0:10:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,...I had no idea why Mona-Lisa-no-Kimi
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.83,0:10:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,...would want to know about Miya-sama and myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.38,0:10:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew nothing of the dark suspicion within her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.24,0:10:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It was... it was all a mystery to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.69,0:10:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But... no matter what... I couldn't have told her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.57,0:10:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This whole matter of my admission into the Sorority...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.84,0:10:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,...even though it was based on misunderstanding,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.96,0:10:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,...about my relationship with you, my brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.86,0:10:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,...and the matter of Miya-sama,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.28,0:10:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't ever tell anyone! How could I!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.95,0:10:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,There has to be something!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.20,0:10:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Something between Miya-sama and Misonoo-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.84,0:10:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Some kind of secret they have to keep hidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.83,0:10:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, and that is Miya-sama's weak point.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.13,0:10:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to find out as quickly as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.21,0:10:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Then we can force Miya-sama to reconsider,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.50,0:10:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,...and she will save the Sorority.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.28,0:11:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we do it? We must.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.14,0:11:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the time to act.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.65,0:11:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.72,0:11:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.78,0:11:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.63,0:11:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This is for the good of the Sorority.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.53,0:11:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If we should fail... the consequences are terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.17,0:11:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps also if we succeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.17,0:11:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.27,0:11:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If we expose Miya-sama's weakness,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.85,0:11:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,...and her position as head of the Sorority becomes untenable,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.71,0:11:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,...so that she cannot continue... then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.41,0:11:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,If that should happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.93,0:11:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,...Ogiwara-san or Komabayashi-san could easily take her place.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.44,0:12:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... Miya-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.80,0:12:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.30,0:12:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It suits you well, Ogiwara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.98,0:12:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The chair of the Sorority leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.56,0:12:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.40,0:12:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have an emergency meeting this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.43,0:12:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Please see that all the members are informed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.77,0:12:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.44,0:12:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.78,0:13:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Your attention please.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.51,0:13:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,All Sorority members please meet at the Sorority house.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.94,0:13:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I repeat,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.40,0:13:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,All Sorority members please meet at the Sorority house.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.13,0:13:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I regret to have to tell you this...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.91,0:13:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a bad apple within our Sorority.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.41,0:13:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,To prevent the whole tree from being ruined,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.87,0:13:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,...this bad apple must be removed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.30,0:13:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll not make a big scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.81,0:13:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Please turn in your resignation immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.17,0:14:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You know who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.08,0:14:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.79,0:14:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,How did this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.63,0:14:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was it? Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.10,0:14:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Who leaked the plan to Miya-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.68,0:14:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be one of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.05,0:14:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to be one of us, because no one else knows!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.44,0:14:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamamoto-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.14,0:14:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You've always been so anxious to please Miya-sama, haven't you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.56,0:14:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.65,0:14:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop pretending.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.24,0:14:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no call for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.99,0:14:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,She would never do such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.64,0:14:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Who, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.86,0:14:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.11,0:14:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.12,0:14:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.63,0:14:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.97,0:15:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.38,0:15:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Accusations won't do any good anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.92,0:15:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Fools. We were all fools.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.71,0:15:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,To think that we could deceive Miya-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.13,0:15:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Compared to Miya-sama, you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.35,0:15:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,...well, let's just say there is no comparison.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.14,0:15:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.34,0:15:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop all this fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.51,0:15:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.60,0:15:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this... is this what you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.66,0:15:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,After all your criticism of Miya-sama? Look at yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.13,0:15:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Yamamoto-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.15,0:15:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll just pretend we don't know anything about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.34,0:15:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's up to you, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.45,0:16:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Fools. Such fools.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.32,0:16:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Do they really imagine the Sorority will let them stay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.58,0:16:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,As far as the bad apples,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.79,0:16:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,...no doubt Miya-sama already knows who they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.28,0:16:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I can't! Leaving the Sorority, the thought of it is just too terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.43,0:16:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Get a grip on yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.11,0:16:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.16,0:16:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.04,0:16:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Misonoo Nanako...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.82,0:16:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,She's the key, we must know her secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.11,0:16:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,This is our last stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.24,0:16:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We will be defeated,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.08,0:16:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,...or Miya-sama herself will be defeated!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.16,0:16:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Misonoo residence.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.18,0:16:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for calling so unexpectedly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.75,0:16:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Mona-Lisa-no-Kimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.34,0:16:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a favor to ask of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.92,0:16:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,A favor?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.87,0:16:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.74,0:17:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The seniors are now discussing the future of the Sorority.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.94,0:17:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I've given the matter a lot of thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.24,0:17:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,...and have come to believe that the Sorority's credibility is ruined beyond repair.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.35,0:17:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That being the case,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.65,0:17:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,...I am prepared to abolish the Sorority.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.30,0:17:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But not everyone is convinced.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.38,0:17:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,As a former member, could you speak to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.35,0:17:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Me? Surely not me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.85,0:17:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you! No one else will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.61,0:17:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But... but!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.61,0:17:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I'll wait for you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.86,0:17:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,My Dear Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.56,0:17:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Mona-Lisa-sama's request was like a dream come true to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.24,0:17:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But... but could I really convince the senior members?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.54,0:17:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.72,0:17:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaoru-no-Kimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.49,0:18:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... where are the other members?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.56,0:18:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,They're inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.98,0:18:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Please go in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.03,0:18:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Mona-Lisa-no-Kimi! What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.36,0:18:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome, Misonoo-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.11,0:18:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Borgia-no-Kimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.06,0:18:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You are so naive!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.75,0:18:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We would never want to abolish the Sorority!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.78,0:18:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We're sorry, Misonoo-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.17,0:18:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's something we have to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.46,0:18:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to tell us the secret between you and Miya-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.15,0:19:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell us. Please tell us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.82,0:19:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,How... how could I?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.85,0:19:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It has nothing to do with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.12,0:19:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It has everything to do with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.41,0:19:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,This secret between you and her... we have to know what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.39,0:19:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't tell us, we are in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.75,0:19:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,All of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.98,0:19:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.47,0:19:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You needn't be so frightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.65,0:19:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Until just recently, you were one of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.40,0:19:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You were a Sorority member.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.62,0:20:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't approve of you as a member.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.83,0:20:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But, I tolerated you, and treated you like the other members.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.05,0:20:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I taught you party etiquette.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.07,0:20:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I taught you flower arranging.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.39,0:20:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I helped you prepare for the exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.91,0:20:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And sometimes... I would even smile at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.10,0:20:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.10,0:20:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Just because Miya-sama favored you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.79,0:20:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,There is something between Miya-sama and you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.38,0:20:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too late to claim you know nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.43,0:20:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? Tell us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.15,0:20:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.97,0:20:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.33,0:20:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't escape either.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.09,0:20:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.10,0:20:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. I know nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.99,0:21:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That can't be true!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.78,0:21:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What can I say to satisfy you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.60,0:21:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.88,0:21:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Miya-sama's secret!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.91,0:21:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, Ogiwara-san. You'll fall! Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.66,0:21:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.01,0:21:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.71,0:21:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Now... Ogiwara-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.49,0:21:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the end... for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.28,0:21:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This is just too awful to bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.50,0:22:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stand it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.98,0:22:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No! No, no! No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.55,0:22:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.94,0:22:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.37,0:22:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I got lost and couldn't find my way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.61,0:22:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,My Dear Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.29,0:22:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Borgia-sama and Mona-Lisa-sama, both of them,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.06,0:22:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,...were nice "big sisters", always taking care of junior members.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.25,0:23:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But they became cornered... desperate...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.17,0:23:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,...they changed... so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.15,0:23:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,My Dear Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.47,0:23:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm collecting signatures to abolish the Sorority.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.39,0:23:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I only want to abolish the Sorority itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.25,0:23:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Please believe me...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.15,0:23:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I am not doing this to hurt individual members.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.78,0:23:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet, my dear brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.46,0:23:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,it seems what I'm doing is the cause of some distress.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.18,0:23:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That hurts me deeply.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.01,0:24:14.21,Ending,,0,0,0,,I dreamed I was chasing a rainbow...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.21,0:24:19.68,Ending,,0,0,0,,Then the rainbow I was chasing was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.15,0:24:25.29,Ending,,0,0,0,,Before, I had no strength, no will.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.29,0:24:30.76,Ending,,0,0,0,,But now because of you, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.50,0:24:37.04,Ending,,0,0,0,,Feelings of love, like raindrops
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.04,0:24:42.51,Ending,,0,0,0,,Come pouring from the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.51,0:24:45.24,Ending,,0,0,0,,This is surely a game
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.24,0:24:48.05,Ending,,0,0,0,,Of some mischievous fairy...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.05,0:24:50.45,Ending,,0,0,0,,Always dancing,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.45,0:24:55.72,Ending,,0,0,0,,Always capricious...
